
######################################################################

TOOLS IMPROVMENTS:
------------------

- PyFlakes 0.9.2.0.1:
	- check "compare has no effect" statements.
	- multiple import on same line
	- re-imports
	- indentation check
	- distinhguish between parameter/variable not used
	
	- and possibility to disable messages through code annotations

- PyMetrics 0.8.2.1:
        - SQLite output
            - " escaped with "", not with \"
            - indices for metricData must are not all 0
            - DROP TABLE, CREATE TABLE with SQLite syntax
        - understand functions defined with only 1 line of code (eg: def toto(): return 1)
        - understand classes defined with only 1 line of code (eg: class tutu: pass)
        - new switch "-y, --quietmoduledocstring" to hide message "module missing doc string" in output
        
        - PythonCodeAnalyserApp comes with a script to insert sql stuff with BEGIN TRANSACTION - END TRANSACTION when filling a DB

